
<div class='container'>
  <div class='row'>
    <div class='col-md-12'>
      <div class='alert alert-warning small'>
        <center><b>Hello and welcome to our Beta testing!</b> The basic functionality is still being developed, therefore not everything you see will work as expected, but updates will come up everyday so that you can test what's new. Please help us turn this platform into something valuable by giving us your feedback! All feedback is important in order to make progress, may it be bugs found, suggestions, or features you want! You can find the feedback button on the left of the page. Thank you!</center>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class='col-md-7 col-md-offset-1'>
      <div id='feeds'>
        {{#if activities}}
          {{#each activities.activityStream}}
            <article class='feed'>
              <div class='wrap'>
                <div class='avatar-outside'>
                  <div class='badge blue-bg'>
                    <span class='icon-favorite-star'></span>
                  </div>
                  <a href='/profile/{{ author._id }}'><img class='authorPicture img-circle' data-src='{{ author.picture }}'></a>
                </div>
                <header>
                  <p>
                    <a class='author' href='/profile/{{ author._id }}'>{{ author.name.full }}</a>
                          {{ verb }}
                          <a class='guide-name' href='/guide/{{ object._id }}'>{{ object.title }}</a>
                          {{ sentence }}
                        </p>
                        <time>
                          <span class='icon icon-clock-time'></span>
                          <p>{{{formatTimezone created}}}</p>
                        </time>
                      </header>
                      <hr>
                      <div class='row'>
                        <div class='col-md-5'>
                          <a href='/guide/{{ object._id }}'>
                            <img class='guidePicture-activity img-responsive' data-src='{{ object.places.0.picture }}'>
                          </a>
                        </div>
                        <div class='col-md-7 right-side'>
                          <a href='/guide/{{ object._id }}'><h1 class='h5 title-route'>{{ object.title }}</h1></a>
                          <p class='description'>{{#if object.description }} {{{trimString object.description 250}}} {{/if}}</p>
                          <div class='user-rating'>
                            <div class='numbers'>
                              {{#if object.avg }} {{ object.avg }} {{else}} 0.0 {{/if}}
                            </div>
                            <div class='rating'>
                              <span>user rating</span>
                              <br>
                              {{ object.votes.length }} votes
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </article>
                {{/each}}
              {{/if}}

